parameters:
Mayor: Gah... you fool...! Do you think there's a mayor
weaker than his citizens?! A mere wrestler like you, beating
me... Take this!!

Shark Broccoli: Guoooooohhhhh!!! Not bad... we're evenly
matched...

Shark Broccoli: I called out the mayor to the ring of the
organization, betting the real power of the city on a one-
on-one battle... This became the prototype for the later
Monster Fights. The battle lasted for hours...

Memimi: There are so many points to interject here, but
let's just go with it for now...

Mayor: Kah... not bad at all... but, gah... as someone
responsible for the lives of the citizens... I can't afford
to fall here... gah...

Mayor: ...Now, my last bit of strength... With this strike,
I'll defeat you...!!

Shark Broccoli: (What determination... Is this what it means
to be a man who stands above others... I am... I am...)

Orca Asparagus: Shark Mountain... Brother Shark Broccoli! I
finally beat down all those councilor lackeys and came to
help!! That was a close one... It's our victory now!!

Shark Broccoli: ...Let's go home, Orca Asparagus... I was
wrong... Continuing the wrestling organization like this is
pointless...

Orca Asparagus: Huh, big bro!? After coming this far, what
are you saying...

Shark Broccoli: In my fight with the mayor, I learned what a
true leader is... I've decided to give up on the loans and
the mayor's seat and turn myself in. However, it seems Orca
Asparagus couldn't accept that until the very end...

Orca Asparagus: Don't mess with me!! If big bro Shark
Mountain won't do it, then I'll become the mayor!!

Shark Broccoli: Listen to me, Orca Mountain...! I'll handle
this so that you won't be implicated... Don't think of such
foolish things!!

Orca Asparagus: You're too soft...! With that attitude, in
the end, you'll lose everything... If it were me... If I
were in charge, I'd do more...

Orca Asparagus: That's right... it's all about money, money!
If you become mayor, you can use taxes however you want, and
if you cut public services, you don't need a budget. It's
not just about wrestling organizations... I can do
anything!!

Shark Broccoli: Orca Asparagus... have you lost your way?
I'm sorry... It's my fault... If I leave things as they are,
I'll end up creating the worst kind of monster...

Orca Asparagus: You're injured, you can't beat me... Our
ties end here!! Enjoy envying my lavish lifestyle from your
poor man's ring!!

Shark Broccoli: The battle lasted for hours... but with the
damage from the fight with the mayor, I was finally defeated
by him... When I woke up, he was already gone... Only his
asparagus, which he never let go of, remained in my hand...

Memimi: There were so many points to question there... but I
think I've got a rough idea of what happened...

Shark Broccoli: Orca Asparagus, who became mayor, devoured
the budget of Dorietoku City relentlessly... It's utterly
frustrating and shameful but... I can no longer resist
anything... It's all my responsibility...

Memimi: No matter what Shark Broccoli Great Leader thinks,
my opinion hasn't changed... I was surprised, but still, you
are a wonderful person.

Memimi: Orca Asparagus... or should I say Mayor Orca... I
will punch him out, break his arrogance, and drag him before
the Great Leader!! With his defeat, he will realize what a
true leader looks like!

Shark Broccoli: Recklessness is... no, I shall say no more.
Duke Shark... I believe in your strength. Save Dorietoku
City... correct my mistakes from that day and rescue me from
these days of regret...!
